Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.99,0:12:43.07,Nazev,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(425,512)\fs30\3c&HE9D1FF&}JUNJOU
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:43.07,Nazev,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(425,512)\fs30\bord4\3c&H3299ED&}JUNJOU
